  27:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****  ===============================================================================
  28:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****   [..]
  29:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****     The UART HAL driver can be used as follows:
  30:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c **** 
  31:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****     (#) Declare a UART_HandleTypeDef handle structure (eg. UART_HandleTypeDef huart).
  32:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****     (#) Initialize the UART low level resources by implementing the HAL_UART_MspInit() API:
  33:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) Enable the USARTx interface clock.
  34:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) UART pins configuration:
  35:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****             (+++) Enable the clock for the UART GPIOs.
  36:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****             (+++) Configure these UART pins as alternate function pull-up.
  37:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) NVIC configuration if you need to use interrupt process (HAL_UART_Transmit_IT()
  38:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****              and HAL_UART_Receive_IT() APIs):
  39:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****             (+++) Configure the USARTx interrupt priority.
  40:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****             (+++) Enable the NVIC USART IRQ handle.
  41:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) UART interrupts handling:
  42:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****               -@@-  The specific UART interrupts (Transmission complete interrupt,
  43:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****                 RXNE interrupt, RX/TX FIFOs related interrupts and Error Interrupts)
  44:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****                 are managed using the macros __HAL_UART_ENABLE_IT() and __HAL_UART_DISABLE_IT()
  45:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****                 inside the transmit and receive processes.
  46:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) DMA Configuration if you need to use DMA process (HAL_UART_Transmit_DMA()
  47:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****              and HAL_UART_Receive_DMA() APIs):
  48:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****             (+++) Declare a DMA handle structure for the Tx/Rx channel.
  49:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****             (+++) Enable the DMAx interface clock.
  50:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****             (+++) Configure the declared DMA handle structure with the required Tx/Rx parameters.
  51:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****             (+++) Configure the DMA Tx/Rx channel.
  52:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****             (+++) Associate the initialized DMA handle to the UART DMA Tx/Rx handle.
  53:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****             (+++) Configure the priority and enable the NVIC for the transfer complete
  54:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****                   interrupt on the DMA Tx/Rx channel.
  55:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c **** 
  56:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****     (#) Program the Baud Rate, Word Length, Stop Bit, Parity, Prescaler value , Hardware
  57:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****         flow control and Mode (Receiver/Transmitter) in the huart handle Init structure.
  58:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c **** 
  59:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****     (#) If required, program UART advanced features (TX/RX pins swap, auto Baud rate detection,...)
  60:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****         in the huart handle AdvancedInit structure.
  61:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c **** 
  62:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****     (#) For the UART asynchronous mode, initialize the UART registers by calling
  63:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****         the HAL_UART_Init() API.
  64:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c **** 
  65:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****     (#) For the UART Half duplex mode, initialize the UART registers by calling
  66:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****         the HAL_HalfDuplex_Init() API.
  67:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c **** 
  68:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****     (#) For the UART LIN (Local Interconnection Network) mode, initialize the UART registers
  69:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****         by calling the HAL_LIN_Init() API.
  70:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c **** 
  71:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****     (#) For the UART Multiprocessor mode, initialize the UART registers
  72:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****         by calling the HAL_MultiProcessor_Init() API.
  73:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c **** 
  74:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****     (#) For the UART RS485 Driver Enabled mode, initialize the UART registers
  75:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****         by calling the HAL_RS485Ex_Init() API.
  76:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c **** 
  77:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****     [..]
  78:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****     (@) These API's (HAL_UART_Init(), HAL_HalfDuplex_Init(), HAL_LIN_Init(), HAL_MultiProcessor_Ini
  79:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****         also configure the low level Hardware GPIO, CLOCK, CORTEX...etc) by
  80:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****         calling the customized HAL_UART_MspInit() API.
  81:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c **** 
