 273:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****     follow respectively the UART asynchronous, UART Half duplex, UART LIN mode
 274:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****     and UART multiprocessor mode configuration procedures (details for the procedures
